text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The US topped the medal table, however, because it had more silver and medals.\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3128, \"end\": 3130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.5652456042904329, \"rank\": 0.7471370089306377, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a news conference on Sunday, Zhou Jinqiang, the vice chief of the Chinese delegation, praised the country's athletes for their \\\"record-breaking performance\\\" as they took home a total of 91 medals.\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3236, \"end\": 3240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_Enlai\", \"score\": 0.9993969613994205, \"rank\": 0.0006025658544548082, \"text\": \"Zhou\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_Enlai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_Enlai\"}, {\"begin\": 3273, \"end\": 3280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9980232956952878, \"rank\": 0.0019512295878578835, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This marks the best result for China in the Olympic Games held overseas since it began participating in the Summer Olympics in 1984,\\\" Zhou said.\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3437, \"end\": 3442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9970224235906049, \"rank\": 0.0029469232715709903, \"text\": \"China\", \